{"tid":1415892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲想救到義士嘛？仲想贏到場運動嘛？","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:53.000Z","uid":199191,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d01b53ee9b6242f12a0e3e3e122ef673158313","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:20:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想嘅全世界唔該冷靜啲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我自己發夢都係企開前面，知道各位手足嘅想法，放火我一定唔會割，我只係想大家停一停！諗一諗！<br />\n<br />\n所有攻擊我地都要有目的性，我留意到多數和理非其實唔反感我地用火去buy time、唔反對我地射狗屋，<br />\n但佢地最介意係我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔禮貌！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白連登好多人都唔在意民意，但五大訴求其實係建基於民意，民意越大，五大訴求越有可能發生，你試想下如果普遍大眾都認為呢次已經變成發洩式行動，到時撤銷所有義士呢個訴求實現起上來，就有難度了<br />\n<br />\n宜家我地需要好好冷靜落嚟，檢討返我地所有行動同對民眾嘅態度，不合作運動又好、游擊戰打法又好，都需要反思檢討。<br />\n<br />\n檢討只為了做得更好，不是想互屌分割<br />\n<br />\n記住我地係人，因為我地有反省能力、有自制力、有原則 ; 但狗比人屌，都為因為佢地不知悔改、失控、冇人性底線<br />\n<br />\n還有，和理非同勇武其實都係同一類人，都只係想要爭取自由嘅同路人，不要互相再標籤了，標籤化本身就係分化的好方法，所以大家不如重新定義一次，以「香港人」呢個身份去抗爭，當我地兩邊都融合成一體，根本連分化的可能都冇<br />\n<br />\n宜家班共狗已經開始玩分化式策略，呢個時候更需要所有人冷靜去面對形勢，去見招拆招<br />\n<br />\n難得我地宜家一手好牌，唔好比港共、林奠、黑社會翻到身可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 6月9開始抗爭，我由612開始嬲到宜家，我都想班仆街死，但戰場上越冷靜一方越大機會生存呢個道理，我相信大家都會明"},{"pid":"9182bcf77fbedffd1e73b07794f6426befc8a975","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"宜家需要文宣組消毒，同埋集中煲大黑社會的惡行<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為機場有得搞，可以大力宣傳下同研究實行方向"},{"pid":"3a2b08e7c117f827bcd5b444587a0d0ee4cc6d0b","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74e58f828c9c907bc4f67cfb0bcf8845a37d3b9c","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c807ed8252b8826c5fcbe7851e6a53945364ae19","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efb1436c8ecbf47a4bc54bceb09195602f7b1a00","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15e01cd907f36802e76013995cf5619145b46095","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0671ed7f81f21b32a814165e2bedda58b4e67f69","tid":1415892,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"同意，幫推"},{"pid":"46dfd7f86b67caff4cd38b0229c5fd5d60544e56","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67cddf7cfc6ec5e3903d71b1e01b8a6951e7a53","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0671ed7f81f21b32a814165e2bedda58b4e67f69","tid":1415892,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"同意，幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"感謝"},{"pid":"b2d3bf7667882375599210aa629f39602e5cebf8","tid":1415892,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"玩得火預左會少一批和理非既支持，什至佢地怕被牽連而唔敢出黎/企咁前。我地唔好忘記和理非同勇武係一脈相通，要做返文宣洗白！"},{"pid":"eece98303700bccae232ce689706ee2d7bba4844","tid":1415892,"uid":239994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"Be humble"},{"pid":"0986869f8ae17d278e489fc4e989461bb75a5049","tid":1415892,"uid":151303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"我不是勇猛隊 不是文人派 更不懂玩弄政治<br />\n我...只是一個 想發一場感化到他人的夢 的女子<br />\n<br />\n經過 前線勇士們 過往的一個月的汗水<br />\n令香港取得 前所未見的 士氣<br />\n<br />\n加上 記者同伴們 鍥而不捨的語言文字<br />\n再令大家 勇於表達自己的聲音<br />\n<br />\n但這一仗 由這天記者會起 將變成長戰<br />\n<br />\n各位 文學家、藝術家和音樂人<br />\n又或是 不停推動本土文化的伙伴們<br />\n<br />\n現在 終於到我們發揮的時候了<br />\n善用 我們的一文一字一書一畫一聲一響一色一彩<br />\n為 義士們錦上添花<br />\n為 長輩們洞悉事理<br />\n為 國外人明晰消息<br />\n為 香港人繼續團結一致<br />\n<br />\n這一個夢....有很多場景...<br />\n<br />\n1) 一日一文宣<br />\n- 由各本地藝術創作者設計<br />\n- 成為民間記者會每天的主題<br />\n- 令新聞話題能每天保持新鮮<br />\n<br />\n2) 人物故事<br />\n- 收集一些真實及動人的故事<br />\n- 以影片方式散播到長輩群<br />\n- 以情打動及讓他們易於體諒和明白<br />\n<br />\n3) 洗腦式運動<br />\n- 由不同的本地音樂人創作歌曲<br />\n- 以實地busking (包括交通工具內) 及影片方式呈現<br />\n- 目的希望 信息易於牢記於心<br />\n<br />\n4) 落地藝術活動<br />\n- 例如 在機場內以可移動式畫廊展示這一個月內的實照<br />\n- 主要針對旅客和沒有參加過活動的港人<br />\n- 讓他們能體會抗爭的處境<br />\n<br />\n我知 此乃冰山一角的夢境<br />\n能發的夢 還有很多的<br />\n香港人 咁多屎橋 那有如此容易認輸 對嗎？"},{"pid":"6195d1fd11c1220062ad59eacc0383352338d6c7","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2d3bf7667882375599210aa629f39602e5cebf8","tid":1415892,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"玩得火預左會少一批和理非既支持，什至佢地怕被牽連而唔敢出黎/企咁前。我地唔好忘記和理非同勇武係一脈相通，要做返文宣洗白！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"明明連登仔應該係最識打鍵戰做文宣，宜家唔發功香土同BBK咪會笑鳩我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲們！做嘢！"},{"pid":"51953a49f3e220cf6e62344b9d89ca6c3c2ac8c0","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"59765c36238c5153198ec1c56f1dbed8c7517970","tid":1415892,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfda2618b7c7ffaa1ec95464011d34124677a4b","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"cc22a9c3799495ab217272d43cadf4910fbbb8bb","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n<br />\n推到多啲人冷靜返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7788ed61f17ef3ffcc14c72664f41f3b7289bb","tid":1415892,"uid":52773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"義士犧牲在所難免<br />\n運動一定要贏"},{"pid":"08ce15bc1f5de27f69bcdbd02ec1288ed336f66c","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"141d315decbb471ac8ce15a529c29c9467aefb9a","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"6b39fe4ea4d896790f301bdcc109ee6bb05c1956","tid":1415892,"uid":253573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"手足們 對住普通市民 要保持禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過埋今晚 全力打文宣戰！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9c77e3dfe9551c89824fbd006a0407c4105e289","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"406bbefb3ac0129759b3d137a2835ae0f09a3d9c","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"b9009a0f1a31cc4a433ef20617f3de9954c60a50","tid":1415892,"uid":199191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"自推十連"}]}